{"word":"Zobah","slug":"zobah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Zobah</b> <a href=\"#/H6678\">H6678</a> <br/> Called also Zoba, Aramzobah, and Hamath-Zobah.<br/> A kingdom in the north of Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=47'>1Sa 14:47</a><br/> Conquest of, by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=8'>2Sa 8:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=12'>2Sa 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=24'>1Ki 11:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=9'>1Ch 18:9</a><br/> Its inhabitants mercenaries of the Ammonites against David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=19'>2Sa 10:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=19&verse=19'>1Ch 19:19</a><br/> David writes a psalm after the conquest of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=60&verse=12'>Psa 60:12</a><br/> Invaded by Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=3'>2Ch 8:3</a>"}]}